name: Mackenzie US Investment Grade Corporate Bond Index ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive Select USD Investment Grade Corporate Hedged to CAD Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in US investment grade corporate bonds issued in US dollars, either directly or indirectly, with its foreign currency exposure hedged back to the Canadian dollar.
